## 🇰🇷 Route: Staying in Korea

You chose to stay in Korea. You locked yourself in your room, studied like crazy, and successfully got into the prestigious high school you always wanted. 

At first, you were thrilled. But soon, the brutal reality hits. The competition is suffocating, the academy schedule never ends, and you realize nothing has truly changed in your life. 

On a rainy night, staring at your math textbook, you look out the window and think:
*"What if I had moved to America back then...?"*

### 🛑 GAME OVER: The Past-Dweller Ending
You spend your youth regretting a path you never took. 

